59
00:02:36,941 --> 00:02:37,680
in the next chapter.

60
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:40,750
Her father, Yan Da Hai,
will conspire against the country

61
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:42,430
to save her.

62
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:46,000
